	<!-- TEXT  -->
	<Language_en_US>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_SRI_PADA_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>Putting Ones Foot In It</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_SRI_PADA_HELP">
			<Text>Glorious Leader, we have a man waiting for you in the audience chamber. He wishes to discuss Sri Pada.[NEWLINE]What shall I tell him?</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_SRI_PADA_HELP_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>The Natural Wonder permanently yields +1 [ICON_CULTURE] Culture and [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_SRI_PADA_HELP_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>The City gains +1 [ICON_PEACE] Faith and +1 [ICON_GOLD] Gold for every Religion which has followers in it.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_SRI_PADA_HELP_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>Lose the -5 [ICON_FOOD] Food from Sri Pada, but gain a copy of [ICON_RES_COFFEE] Coffee and [ICON_RES_TEA] Tea.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_SRI_PADA_HELP_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>Place strict regulations on polluting industry, Factories and Coal Plants constructed in the City have -3 [ICON_PRODUCTION] Production and -3 [ICON_GOLD] Gold.[NEWLINE]Butterflies in your Empire's Zoos cause them to yield +1 [ICON_RESEARCH] Science and +1 [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_SRI_PADA_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>*The man wishes to discuss the construction of a small shrine on the mountain, to honor his ancestors*[NEWLINE]To honor one's ancestors is a noble cause. We shall not refuse our subject.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_SRI_PADA_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>*The visitor is a priest, he wishes for you to prevent other faiths from ascending the mountain*[NEWLINE]How ignorant of this man! Sri Pada is held sacred by many varied and peaceful causes, I shall not take issue with them for his own vanity.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_SRI_PADA_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>*The petition turns out to be from a merchant: he wishes to replace the paddy fields on the mountain's slopes with plantations of expensive, tropical plants like Tea and Coffee*[NEWLINE]The food supply of the City is adequate, we support this plan.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_SRI_PADA_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>*The woman comes on the recommendation of the Science Advisor. She is campaigning for the protection and study of the mountains unique butterfly population*[NEWLINE]What would this protection scheme involve, exactly? I am a big fan of butterflies.</Text>
		</Row>

		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_BUILDING_NW_SRI_PADA_DUMMY">
			<Text>A Spiritual Meaning</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_BUILDING_NW_SRI_PADA_DUMMY_HELP">
			<Text>+1 [ICON_PEACE] Faith and +1 [ICON_GOLD] Gold for every Religion that has followers inside the City.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_BUILDING_NW_SRI_PADA_DUMMY_2">
			<Text>Butterflies Charter</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_BUILDING_NW_SRI_PADA_DUMMY_2_HELP">
			<Text>+1 [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism and [ICON_RESEARCH] Science to Zoos.</Text>
		</Row>
	</Language_en_US>
